summary: adds more plant life to Solitude to those areas that looked oddly empty
descriptionHtml:

If you wish to Upload images feel free to 



File changes now located in change log.



Description

Adds more trees and other flora and plants to Solitude to improve the atmosphere of the town. The mod also adds more street lamps to the city  as well. I\'ll most likely continue this mod and tweak it over time.



Requirements

Skyrim (of course :P )
